# 07.08 Product Summary

## Overview

The Product Summary provides a complete overview of how cmdOS transforms its underlying architecture and development foundation into a complete AI Execution Operating System product ecosystem.

cmdOS is designed to redefine how humans interact with computers.

Instead of users operating applications manually, cmdOS enables users to express intent and allows AI systems to understand, plan, and execute tasks.

Core principle:

Human Intent

↓

AI Understanding

↓

Agent Planning

↓

Capability Selection

↓

Execution

↓

Result

