# 1. Product Architecture Summary

The cmdOS product ecosystem consists of multiple interconnected layers.

---

# User Experience Layer

Purpose:

Provide natural interaction between humans and cmdOS.

Includes:

- CMD interface
- Desktop interface
- Mobile interface
- Voice interaction

---

# AI Intelligence Layer

Purpose:

Understand user goals and generate solutions.

Includes:

- Intent recognition
- Reasoning
- Context understanding
- Decision making

---

# Agent Layer

Purpose:

Provide autonomous execution.

Includes:

- Personal Agents
- Business Agents
- Enterprise Agents
- Specialized Agents

---

# Capability Layer

Purpose:

Provide executable actions.

Includes:

- Applications
- APIs
- Plugins
- External services

---

# Execution Layer

Purpose:

Transform AI decisions into real-world actions.

Includes:

- Desktop execution
- Mobile execution
- Workflow automation
- System operations

